"CWE-125";"CVE-2017-12985";"https://github.com/the-tcpdump-group/tcpdump/commit/66df248b49095c261138b5a5e34d341a6bf9ac7f";"CVE-2017-12985/IPv6: Check for print routines returning -1 when running past the end.

